[
  {
    "text": "Life is hard.",
    "start": 0.72,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Especially if you’re a flesh-eating zombie.",
    "start": 2.32,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "That’s why we’ve come up with",
    "start": 4.8,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "food hacks the undead can’t get enough of.",
    "start": 7.04,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Must. Get. Food.",
    "start": 11.44,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh?",
    "start": 17.52,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Is this even food?",
    "start": 18.56,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Uhhhh.",
    "start": 23.72,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "This is gross.",
    "start": 24.72,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Stupid gluten-free garbage.",
    "start": 26.64,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Anything bloody in here?",
    "start": 29.68,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Ugh.",
    "start": 31.36,
    "duration": 2.018
  },
  {
    "text": "AHHHHH!!!",
    "start": 33.378,
    "duration": 4.542
  },
  {
    "text": "NO!!",
    "start": 37.92,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "AHHHHH!!!",
    "start": 41.32,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you okay?!",
    "start": 42.32,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "I need to eat, like, NOW.",
    "start": 43.52,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "No wonder you’re moody.",
    "start": 48.8,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah?",
    "start": 53.28,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "You like these?",
    "start": 53.92,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Don’t bite me, okay?",
    "start": 55.04,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "What do you think?",
    "start": 56.64,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, something salty then!",
    "start": 58.08,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Please stop yelling!!",
    "start": 65.44,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Everyone likes these!",
    "start": 67.28,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you kidding me?!",
    "start": 74.32,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "I’m really trying here, okay!",
    "start": 76.16,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course!",
    "start": 80.08,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Why didn’t I think of this before?!",
    "start": 81.12,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "First pour some milk into a bowl.",
    "start": 85.52,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Then add in some gelatin.",
    "start": 87.76,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Stir it up really well.",
    "start": 91.68,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Once that’s done,",
    "start": 96.48,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Add some pink and brown food coloring.",
    "start": 97.6,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Now pour it into a glass.",
    "start": 102.64,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "A funnel makes it less messy.",
    "start": 104.4,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Then stick in a handful of straws.",
    "start": 109.44,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "And off to the fridge it goes!",
    "start": 113.36,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Now for the best part.",
    "start": 115.76,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Smashy smashy!",
    "start": 117.44,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Then pour the crumbs into a bowl.",
    "start": 121.12,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember those straws?",
    "start": 123.68,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Now they’re edible worms!",
    "start": 125.36,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "They look pretty real, don’t they?",
    "start": 131.84,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, Lizzy?",
    "start": 134.32,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Still hungry?",
    "start": 135.6,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Worms.",
    "start": 137.36,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "They’re still alive too…",
    "start": 138.8,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Mmmm.",
    "start": 144.84,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Covered in fresh dirt too.",
    "start": 145.84,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "They’re pretty tasty, huh?",
    "start": 148.88,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Guess we’re not using a fork today.",
    "start": 152.0,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow, that’s a big bite there!",
    "start": 158.72,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "That really hit the spot, Tina.",
    "start": 161.44,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "AHHHHH!!!",
    "start": 167.48,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Chill, my dude, I have a ticket!",
    "start": 168.48,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Enjoy the movie.",
    "start": 171.68,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi there!",
    "start": 175.04,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Two, please!",
    "start": 175.84,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "No candy allowed.",
    "start": 177.28,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I don’t make the rules.",
    "start": 179.2,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Can’t bring that stuff in.",
    "start": 180.56,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Woah!",
    "start": 186.96,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 189.36,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, just hold these.",
    "start": 190.48,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "All we need is an extra hand!",
    "start": 193.28,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "AHH!!!",
    "start": 195.96,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Where’d you get that?",
    "start": 196.96,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "It’s fake?",
    "start": 199.76,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "That’s genius!",
    "start": 201.28,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Can it fit all our candy?",
    "start": 203.2,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure it’s packed in there…",
    "start": 208.64,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Really holds onto it, huh?",
    "start": 211.2,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Now for the perfect placement…",
    "start": 214.8,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Beautiful.",
    "start": 218.24,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "I’ll act natural, don’t worry.",
    "start": 219.6,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey!",
    "start": 223.04,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "You want this to work or not?",
    "start": 224.4,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Can we go in now, please?",
    "start": 226.88,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Alrighty.",
    "start": 230.32,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "You don’t have any snacks, right?",
    "start": 231.44,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "You’d better not be hiding anything.",
    "start": 233.28,
    "duration": 6.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh boy.",
    "start": 245.28,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "I didn’t see that coming.",
    "start": 246.4,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh, thanks, security guy!",
    "start": 250.96,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "I think I figured this guy out!",
    "start": 263.6,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes.",
    "start": 265.6,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "You having trouble, Lizzy?",
    "start": 266.8,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe no more chewing…",
    "start": 269.6,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "You really are having trouble, huh?",
    "start": 271.92,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "A little energy boost ought to help!",
    "start": 274.8,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Consider it brain food!",
    "start": 279.84,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Brains?",
    "start": 282.08,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Count me in!",
    "start": 283.36,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And?",
    "start": 287.84,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Delicious!",
    "start": 289.04,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, answer, come to me….",
    "start": 290.8,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "I dunno…",
    "start": 294.88,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Still feeling sluggish, huh?",
    "start": 296.88,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe something healthier.",
    "start": 299.52,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "I can almost see the answer now!",
    "start": 307.76,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on….",
    "start": 310.32,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Your stupid food is worthless!",
    "start": 315.12,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, yea?",
    "start": 318.72,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Try this thing on for size.",
    "start": 321.44,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Where is that thing?",
    "start": 324.72,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "I have something you’ll like!",
    "start": 327.76,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "BINGO!!",
    "start": 329.84,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "This thing’s fresh.",
    "start": 331.36,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Mmm!!!",
    "start": 336.36,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "It’s already working, I know it!",
    "start": 337.36,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Wanna make your own brains?",
    "start": 342.48,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Roll your confectionary mastic into a ball.",
    "start": 344.24,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Then use a skewer to make \nan indent down its middle.",
    "start": 346.8,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Then put a squiggly piece like this",
    "start": 353.36,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "on top of one half.",
    "start": 355.52,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Then do the same thing on the other side.",
    "start": 359.04,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Looks a lot like brains to me!",
    "start": 362.72,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "I’m like a zombie snack genius!",
    "start": 365.36,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Think you know the answer?",
    "start": 367.84,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Check it out!",
    "start": 370.24,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I’m a chef, not a magician.",
    "start": 378.24,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Everyone knows a hungry zombie",
    "start": 383.76,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "is a sad zombie.",
    "start": 386.08,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "What kind of color is this?",
    "start": 388.16,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "If it isn’t blood red, I don’t want it.",
    "start": 390.48,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Is she looking?",
    "start": 393.44,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Time for some fun!",
    "start": 394.96,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I see a perfect prank in our midst!",
    "start": 396.72,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "She’s coming back!",
    "start": 402.72,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Don’t eat too fast, okay?",
    "start": 404.16,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "She’ll never see this coming!",
    "start": 407.44,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Bon appetite!",
    "start": 409.92,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh-huh.",
    "start": 414.36,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Is there pepper in this?",
    "start": 415.36,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "I think I'm gonna…",
    "start": 417.36,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah-ah-ah -ah",
    "start": 421.84,
    "duration": 2.993
  },
  {
    "text": "CHOO!",
    "start": 424.833,
    "duration": 1.247
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on!",
    "start": 426.08,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Lizzy?",
    "start": 427.76,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Is that your eyeball?!!",
    "start": 428.8,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "How hard was that sneeze?!",
    "start": 430.64,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "I’m so scared, ah!",
    "start": 432.72,
    "duration": 4.12
  },
  {
    "text": "It’s just an eye, Tina.",
    "start": 437.36,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "C’mere, little guy.",
    "start": 441.2,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "So slippery.",
    "start": 442.96,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I hate my eyes fall out, you?",
    "start": 446.16,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh god….",
    "start": 449.12,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Smells good.",
    "start": 451.76,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Did you just eat your eyeball?",
    "start": 455.52,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Want to try this trick yourself?",
    "start": 458.64,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Cut a hard-boiled egg in half.",
    "start": 460.48,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Use one of these to make a hole.",
    "start": 465.04,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "That way you’ll have room for a green olive.",
    "start": 469.92,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Stick that sucker in,",
    "start": 472.24,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "And use a straw",
    "start": 474.24,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "to cut out a chunk of black olive.",
    "start": 475.28,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Then carefully place it here.",
    "start": 479.2,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Use a brush and red food coloring",
    "start": 481.76,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "to mark up the white of the eye.",
    "start": 483.6,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you’ve made a pair,",
    "start": 487.76,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Use gelatin to cover the eyes.",
    "start": 488.88,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "You want them gooey, right?",
    "start": 493.36,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Looks like they’re ready!",
    "start": 495.12,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Wanna know something funny?",
    "start": 497.44,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Do these look like mine?",
    "start": 499.68,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 504.48,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Just a little food trickery for ya.",
    "start": 505.76,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Try it!",
    "start": 508.72,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh, okay…   ",
    "start": 510.56,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "That’s not half bad!   \nCan we make a couple more?   ",
    "start": 514.48,
    "duration": 4.008
  },
  {
    "text": "Ever seen a mug this crazy?",
    "start": 522.48,
    "duration": 2.508
  },
  {
    "text": "You’re the funniest zombie I know!",
    "start": 525.553,
    "duration": 2.513
  },
  {
    "text": "The food!",
    "start": 528.96,
    "duration": 1.141
  },
  {
    "text": "Gorgeous marshmallows   for a gorgeous lady.",
    "start": 530.101,
    "duration": 3.275
  },
  {
    "text": "Are these homemade?",
    "start": 535.0,
    "duration": 1.469
  },
  {
    "text": "Only the finest for you, miss.",
    "start": 536.812,
    "duration": 2.331
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh?   What is this?   Tina? \n  Remember the face?!   ",
    "start": 540.72,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Since when did I turn into the third wheel?  ",
    "start": 545.76,
    "duration": 3.043
  },
  {
    "text": "I've gotta get her attention back.",
    "start": 549.079,
    "duration": 1.996
  },
  {
    "text": "At least I’ve got these to munch on.",
    "start": 551.822,
    "duration": 2.522
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait!   I know just what to do!  \nThis zombie’s about to get crafty!   ",
    "start": 557.44,
    "duration": 5.824
  },
  {
    "text": "Yep, just a few more folds…",
    "start": 565.68,
    "duration": 2.099
  },
  {
    "text": "My favorite colored condiment!",
    "start": 568.001,
    "duration": 1.981
  },
  {
    "text": "Time to dig in!",
    "start": 571.28,
    "duration": 1.653
  },
  {
    "text": "Bloody bone, anyone?",
    "start": 573.014,
    "duration": 2.03
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at my bone, Tina!",
    "start": 575.932,
    "duration": 2.012
  },
  {
    "text": "Um…",
    "start": 578.542,
    "duration": 1.177
  },
  {
    "text": "I think somethings \nwrong with your friend.",
    "start": 580.64,
    "duration": 2.425
  },
  {
    "text": "Who, me?",
    "start": 583.44,
    "duration": 1.617
  },
  {
    "text": "I have three more!",
    "start": 585.057,
    "duration": 2.077
  },
  {
    "text": "AHH!!!",
    "start": 587.134,
    "duration": 2.866
  },
  {
    "text": "At least I have their attention.",
    "start": 590.0,
    "duration": 2.224
  },
  {
    "text": "Suddenly feeling hungry for \nsome zombie-friendly snacks?",
    "start": 594.72,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "We don’t blame you! Share this with your \nfriends so they can try these treats too!",
    "start": 597.84,
    "duration": 4.648
  }
]